WEBVTT

00:11:29.301 --> 00:11:30.976
of the economic collapse,

00:11:31.000 --> 00:11:34.976
is that too many organizations
are making their decisions,

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:37.372
their policies about talent and people,

00:11:37.396 --> 00:11:41.523
based on assumptions that are outdated,

00:11:41.547 --> 00:11:42.737
unexamined,

00:11:42.761 --> 00:11:45.523
and rooted more in folklore
than in science.

00:11:46.404 --> 00:11:48.976
And if we really want to get
out of this economic mess,

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:51.093
if we really want high performance

00:11:51.117 --> 00:11:53.564
on those definitional tasks
of the 21st century,

00:11:53.588 --> 00:11:59.528
the solution is not to do
more of the wrong things,

00:11:59.552 --> 00:12:01.875
to entice people with a sweeter carrot,